  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5735831/" class="title-link">鼓掌——给李鸿章的为官之道</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5735831"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/leyyleyy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u40830911-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leyyleyy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">乐悠悠</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-11"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-11 13:24:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5735831_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      “敌人，只有敌人，才有可能为你创造机会。而你的战友和同伴，都是和你争夺机会的人。” 这句话狠狠震了我一记，通常我听到的是“要感谢你的敌人”，因为他们的刁难、打击，给了你实战经验，这原理跟“失败乃成功之母”差不多。但是，没想过“战友和同伴”往往也是竞争对手...

